Function to randomly set the priors

random_priors.Rd

Assign random priors. This is mostly used with the simulate_disease() function.

Usage

random_priors(...)

Arguments

...

Any parameter used in set_priors() that will remain fixed (not random).

Examples

#Get random priors
random_priors()
